<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Website Features | FTP File Transfer</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="features-style.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1037/1037316.png" type="image/png">
    <style>
    /* General Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    background-image: url(" https://getsynccom.wpenginepowered.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shutterstock_1901165272-1536x758.jpg");
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.features-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
}

header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 20px;
}

.features-heading {
    font-size: 36px;
    color: #3498db;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.intro-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #3498db;
}

/* Features Section */
.features-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-around;
    padding: 50px 0;
}

.feature-box {
    background-color: white;
    width: 300px;
    margin: 20px;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: slideUp 1s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
}

.feature-box h2 {
    color: #3498db;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.feature-box p {
    color: #7f8c8d;
}

/* Hover Effects */
.feature-box:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

/* Footer */
.features-footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px;
    background-color: #3498db;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Animations */
@keyframes slideUp {
    0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

/* Animation Delays */
.feature-box:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
}
.feature-box:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
}
.feature-box:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.7s;
}
.feature-box:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
}
.feature-box:nth-child(5) {
    animation-delay: 1.1s;
}
.feature-box:nth-child(6) {
    animation-delay: 1.3s;
}

/* Responsive Styles */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-section {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .feature-box {
        width: 80%;
    }
}
    
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="features-container">
        <header>
            <h1 class="features-heading">Website Features</h1>
            <p class="intro-text">Explore the advanced features of our file transfer platform using FTP technology.</p>
        </header>

        <section class="features-section">
            <div class="feature-box animate-feature">
                <h2>High-Speed File Transfers</h2>
                <p>Our FTP server is optimized for high-speed transfers, enabling quick file uploads and downloads, even for large files.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box animate-feature">
                <h2>Reliable Data Transfer</h2>
                <p>Our FTP solution ensures reliable file transfers, allowing interrupted transfers to resume and ensuring data integrity.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box animate-feature">
                <h2>Secure with FTPS Encryption</h2>
                <p>Your data is encrypted during transfer using FTPS, ensuring all file transmissions are secure from unauthorized access.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box animate-feature">
                <h2>Cross-Platform Compatibility</h2>
                <p>Our FTP system works seamlessly on Windows, macOS, and Linux, supporting various FTP clients for ease of use.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box animate-feature">
                <h2>Multi-User Support</h2>
                <p>Collaborate with your team in real-time. Our FTP system supports multiple users and simultaneous file transfers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box animate-feature">
                <h2>File Integrity Check</h2>
                <p>We use automated file integrity checks to ensure that your files are accurately transferred without any data loss.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="features-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 X Transfer Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
	